      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAY KEEPING (2) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing fourth (30.30) in a Grade 5 at this track. Normally fast to begin but shuffled back last time. Got the money at her only try from this box. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. GALBA MODEL (1) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at this track the following run. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. WAX AND WASH (8) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in his powerful 24.49 win at Goulburn over 440m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. BANDIT LYNNE (5) has ability and looks a top-three prospect.",
